From 01c2e217a8d21aa2aec544d99dedcfe5f895f10b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Pandaa Xi <tavut846@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 15 Jun 2026 01:32:45 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] feat: add AnyTLS protocol support (inbound + outbound)

- proxy/anytls: full inbound (server.go) and outbound (client.go) handlers
- proxy/anytls/session: session mux, stream, padding, pipe, client pool
- proxy/anytls/account.go: MemoryAccount + Validator keyed by sha256(password)
- proxy/anytls/config.pb.go: hand-crafted protobuf (Account, ClientConfig, ServerConfig)
- infra/conf/anytls.go: JSON config builder for anytls inbound/outbound
- infra/conf/xray.go: register "anytls" in inbound/outbound loader maps
- main/distro/all/all.go: import proxy/anytls to trigger init()

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
